  "title": "Sales Promoter",
  "description": "<p>Location: 118 Aljunied Ave 2 or any other roadshow locations</p><p>Employment Type: Part-time / Contract</p><p>Start Date: Immediate</p><p></p><p><strong>About Iron Scholars</strong></p><p>Iron Scholars is an enrichment centre in Aljunied, Singapore, dedicated to nurturing young minds through abacus, brain training, STEAM learning and language learning. Our programmes inspire curiosity, confidence, and a love for learning. Learn more at www.ironscholars.com.</p><p></p><p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><p>We are looking for <strong>results-driven</strong> Sales Promoters to represent Iron Scholars at roadshows and events. Your main goal is not just to hand out flyers, it’s to secure trial sign-ups and close deals for enrolment packages.</p><p>This role is ideal for someone with a strong sales mindset, persuasive communication skills, and the ability to build trust quickly with parents.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• \tActively engage parents and families at roadshows, confidently presenting Iron Scholars’ programmes.</p><p>• \tDrive trial class sign-ups and ensure follow-through to actual attendance.</p><p>• \tConvert trial participants into enrolment package deals, handling objections and highlighting programme value.</p><p>• \tTrack sign-ups and provide accurate reporting of conversions.</p><p>• \tRepresent Iron Scholars with professionalism and enthusiasm.</p><p></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• \tProven ability to close sales in roadshow or face-to-face settings.</p><p>• \tStrong communication and persuasion skills.</p><p>• \tOutgoing personality with energy to engage families.</p><p>• \tPrior experience in sales, education promotion, or events preferred.</p><p>• \tFlexible to work evenings and weekends.</p><p></p><p><strong>Compensation</strong></p><p>• \tBase Pay: $10/hour</p><p>• \tCommission:</p><p>• \t$5 per confirmed trial sign-up (with attendance)</p><p>• \t$20 per confirmed registration for our enrolment package</p><p>• \tPerformance Bonus: Additional $50 incentives for hitting 10 enrolments per roadshow.</p><p></p><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><p>• \tTraining on Iron Scholars’ programmes.</p><p>• \tCompetitive commission structure with clear emphasis on closing deals.</p><p>• \tOpportunities to grow with a forward-thinking education brand.</p><p>• \tSupportive team environment that values initiative and results.</p>",
